01:00:26.402 --> 01:00:27.203
in a Sunday school class.

01:00:27.443 --> 01:00:31.247
And I'm glad I jumped on the gospel train then, because that's the only time it came around to my station.

01:00:34.992 --> 01:00:37.374
But I began to feel something's missing, something's wrong.

01:00:37.414 --> 01:00:43.461
I even vieded some folks from the Presbyterian Church to come to my house and talk with me.

01:00:43.541 --> 01:00:47.406
And they came and they were nice people and they were kind enough to come.

01:00:47.446 --> 01:00:49.028
And so I appreciate that.

01:00:49.408 --> 01:00:52.011
And they kind of just talked with me and so forth and so on.

01:00:52.071 --> 01:00:53.653
And I thank them.

01:00:53.673 --> 01:00:54.674
But when they left,

01:00:54.978 --> 01:00:58.321
In my heart, I felt like that's nice, but that's not it.

01:00:59.903 --> 01:01:00.683
That's not it.

01:01:01.284 --> 01:01:04.787
And I remember I went to my bedroom upstairs in the house.

01:01:05.488 --> 01:01:06.289
I lived with my parents.

01:01:07.009 --> 01:01:13.095
I was a student, went upstairs, and I just knelt down and prayed, and I said, God, I don't know what it is.

01:01:13.996 --> 01:01:15.597
But there's got to be more than this.

01:01:16.939 --> 01:01:22.144
I mean, when I thumb through the pages of the book of Acts, I see a different church.

01:01:23.605 --> 01:01:24.786
I see a church with power.

01:01:25.506 --> 01:01:26.868
I see a church that's bold.

01:01:27.649 --> 01:01:29.972
I see signs and wonders and miracles.

01:01:30.052 --> 01:01:31.975
Supernatural things are happening.

01:01:32.055 --> 01:01:36.100
I see the fire of God and I'm not seeing that.

01:01:36.241 --> 01:01:37.322
I'm not seeing that in my life.

01:01:38.484 --> 01:01:43.070
I could never stand in front of you like I'm doing today and talk about Jesus.

01:01:43.150 --> 01:01:44.171
I was just too scared.

01:01:44.472 --> 01:01:46.334
I was just too nervous.

01:01:46.394 --> 01:01:47.556
I was just afraid.

01:01:47.776 --> 01:01:52.082
And I said, there's got to be something more.

01:01:53.346 --> 01:01:55.830
And the Lord orchestrated some things in my life.

01:01:55.850 --> 01:01:57.814
You know, when you call to him, he will hear you.

01:01:59.076 --> 01:02:02.381
Remember that Jesus said, if any man thirst, let him come to me and drink.

01:02:03.523 --> 01:02:07.710
That means one of the prerequisites to being filled with spirit is desire.

01:02:09.473 --> 01:02:17.106
Honestly, I'm trying to give you some instruction to strengthen your confidence, but I can't make you desire anything.

01:02:18.274 --> 01:02:24.986
You know, if we have to, like, hit you over there with a baseball bat before you want anything from God, I think you'd be better off going to Longhorn this morning.

01:02:26.690 --> 01:02:28.433
You're in the wrong place.

01:02:28.453 --> 01:02:30.737
I think some people are not filled because they don't want it.

01:02:31.238 --> 01:02:32.861
They don't want more of the Holy Spirit.

01:02:33.623 --> 01:02:37.149
I didn't know anything, but I knew something.

01:02:37.670 --> 01:02:38.391
I need something.

01:02:39.333 --> 01:02:41.938
I attended a young people's meeting.

01:02:42.146 --> 01:02:48.712
And I shared with one brother that I met there, my feelings, what I was going through, my sense of weakness, my discouragement.

01:02:49.193 --> 01:02:52.576
And right off the bat, thank God for people that are just very frank.

01:02:52.596 --> 01:02:55.118
That's why I think I'm frank with you because that helped me.

01:02:55.498 --> 01:02:57.440
He said, have you been baptized with the Holy Spirit?

01:02:58.721 --> 01:03:00.103
I had no idea what that means.

01:03:00.763 --> 01:03:02.105
Though I've been in church 16 years.

01:03:03.146 --> 01:03:05.087
I was born one week, I was in church the next week.

01:03:06.689 --> 01:03:10.853
You know, from nursery all the way through, young people, everything, never heard that before.

01:03:10.873 --> 01:03:12.114
I have no idea what he's talking about.

01:03:12.802 --> 01:03:15.465
And in the Presbyterian Church, they baptized infants.

01:03:15.945 --> 01:03:19.408
So he said, if he had baptized all his spirits, I said, well, I was baptized, but I was an infant.

01:03:19.428 --> 01:03:21.030
He said, no, I'm not talking about that.

01:03:21.470 --> 01:03:22.732
Then he said, do you speak in tongues?

01:03:23.312 --> 01:03:25.694
And I honestly answered and said, I'm studying French.

01:03:29.338 --> 01:03:30.039
I'm not joking.

01:03:30.079 --> 01:03:31.040
That's what I answered.

01:03:34.363 --> 01:03:35.824
In school, I was taking a class in French.

01:03:36.064 --> 01:03:37.686
And he said, no, no, I'm talking about other tongues.

01:03:37.726 --> 01:03:39.608
And I said, no idea.

01:03:40.989 --> 01:03:41.970
He said, that's what you need.

01:03:42.754 --> 01:03:44.557
I was like, wow, wow.

01:03:45.137 --> 01:03:48.963
But then there were other voices out there.

01:03:49.724 --> 01:03:53.269
And some people, you know, some people can be very generous with their opinions, right?

01:03:53.309 --> 01:03:54.891
Especially when you're, when you're hurting.

01:03:55.231 --> 01:03:58.576
And some people said, well, there is a map solely spirits don't just speak in tongues.

01:03:58.596 --> 01:04:05.746
Other people said, you know, another thing that's not even for us a day that when you got saved, you got all there is that's all period.

01:04:05.890 --> 01:04:07.212
you know, finish.

01:04:07.893 --> 01:04:13.241
And so I was confused and somebody even gave me a book, you know, entitled Doubt and Unbelief or something like that.

01:04:13.261 --> 01:04:16.726
And so I was confused and I was praying now.

01:04:17.407 --> 01:04:19.350
I went back to my own little upper room.

01:04:19.390 --> 01:04:23.617
I went up to my bedroom again and I said, so many voices.

01:04:23.697 --> 01:04:26.661
And I said, God, I don't know what's right, what's not right.

01:04:27.422 --> 01:04:29.706
And I said, you have to give me a sign, show me.

01:04:30.527 --> 01:04:35.154
Well, a day or so later, I was in the large cafeteria

01:04:35.234 --> 01:04:37.957
on campus that could seat, I guess, hundreds of students.

01:04:38.638 --> 01:04:52.473
And student organizations advertised different meetings they had, and someone had put a banner, a large banner, on the wall that said, come get filled with the Holy Spirit today at 2 p.m.

01:04:52.533 --> 01:04:53.875
I think it was room 202.

01:04:56.297 --> 01:04:58.119
And I prayed that God would give me a sign.

01:04:58.140 --> 01:05:01.423
I had no idea what actually would be a literal sign right there on the wall.

01:05:02.805 --> 01:05:03.986
And so I went.

01:05:05.410 --> 01:05:09.836
And there's a small little group of fellows meeting for prayer that I found out later.

01:05:09.896 --> 01:05:11.959
They met every Tuesday or whatever it was.

01:05:12.040 --> 01:05:13.802
And I was the only visitor.

01:05:14.663 --> 01:05:16.746
So, you know, they were kind of eyeing me.

01:05:16.927 --> 01:05:17.527
They were looking at me.

01:05:17.888 --> 01:05:22.635
And so one brother got up there and he went through several scriptures to be honest with you.

01:05:22.995 --> 01:05:25.459
It went in one ear and out another.

01:05:25.860 --> 01:05:27.602
I don't remember a word he said.

01:05:28.162 --> 01:05:30.624
And I didn't comprehend anything.

01:05:30.644 --> 01:05:32.967
He said, some of you, maybe that's your testimony today.

01:05:33.447 --> 01:05:37.271
And I don't know what he said.

01:05:37.551 --> 01:05:39.713
I don't know anything, right?

01:05:40.434 --> 01:05:43.497
And then he looked right at me because I'm the only visitor.

01:05:44.458 --> 01:05:46.700
And he said, so can we pray for you?

01:05:48.682 --> 01:05:50.364
And there was a hush over the crowd.

01:05:50.944 --> 01:05:52.686
There was a nervous tension in the air.

01:05:53.186 --> 01:05:56.850
And I said, yeah, that's why I came.

01:06:00.290 --> 01:06:03.334
And they all kind of had relief.

01:06:04.175 --> 01:06:06.097
And so they kind of surrounded me.

01:06:06.618 --> 01:06:10.062
There had to be like, I don't know, six or seven or more of them.

01:06:10.683 --> 01:06:12.365
And they said, OK, we're going to lay hands on you.

01:06:13.066 --> 01:06:13.707
Pray this prayer.

01:06:13.847 --> 01:06:17.893
And I'm like, bring it on.

01:06:17.913 --> 01:06:22.498
I'm ready because this is what I've been praying about and concerned about, bring it on.

01:06:23.019 --> 01:06:24.221
And so they laid hands on me.

01:06:25.362 --> 01:06:28.466
And to be honest, I did kind of feel something

01:06:29.378 --> 01:06:32.423
But I thought to myself, but I've felt that before.

01:06:33.525 --> 01:06:39.374
Even in the Presbyterian church, like from time to time, I kind of felt a little something like that before.

01:06:39.434 --> 01:06:44.002
If you can feel something like that in the Presbyterian church, God loves you.

01:06:44.442 --> 01:06:54.258
And they said, now speak in tongues.

01:06:57.026 --> 01:07:02.053
And I'm thinking, yeah, but if I knew how to do that, I wouldn't be here in the first place asking you to pray for me.

01:07:02.733 --> 01:07:04.135
And so I said, hallelujah, hallelujah.

01:07:04.155 --> 01:07:05.837
They said, no, no, no, no, they stopped.

01:07:06.158 --> 01:07:06.799
No, hallelujah.

01:07:07.239 --> 01:07:08.040
Speak in tongues.

01:07:11.304 --> 01:07:11.865
Just start.

01:07:13.487 --> 01:07:13.587
Okay.

01:07:13.607 --> 01:07:15.910
So they all praying in tongues, laying hands when they're praying in tongues.

01:07:15.930 --> 01:07:17.492
I'm like, whoa, that is something.

01:07:17.553 --> 01:07:18.554
That's something.

01:07:18.574 --> 01:07:18.674
Yeah.

01:07:18.754 --> 01:07:19.635
Okay, that's it.

01:07:19.675 --> 01:07:19.935
That's it.

01:07:19.975 --> 01:07:20.897
We are here.

01:07:21.017 --> 01:07:22.959
We are with the fanatics right now.

01:07:26.023 --> 01:07:27.765
What have I got myself into?

01:07:28.646 --> 01:07:33.051
And they stopped three different times.

01:07:33.992 --> 01:07:35.093
They were old school.

01:07:36.715 --> 01:07:38.417
They didn't say, well, we believe you have it.

01:07:38.958 --> 01:07:39.598
See you next Sunday.

01:07:39.638 --> 01:07:41.441
No, no, they are old school.

01:07:41.701 --> 01:07:42.362
You're going to get it.

01:07:44.044 --> 01:07:44.744
That was good for me.

01:07:44.825 --> 01:07:46.066
I needed that.

01:07:46.626 --> 01:07:51.211
And I realized after some time that they're not going to stop.

01:07:52.532 --> 01:07:54.694
We're going to be here to the cows come home.

01:07:54.874 --> 01:07:55.735
We're not going to stop.

01:07:56.496 --> 01:07:59.439
And I don't know what kind of mess I've gotten myself into.

01:07:59.459 --> 01:08:02.322
And I thought, I better say something.

01:08:02.722 --> 01:08:05.545
Because if I don't say something, I'll never get out of here.

01:08:05.805 --> 01:08:09.870
Who knows about these fanatics, what they're going to do next?

01:08:12.032 --> 01:08:14.194
And directly like some little

01:08:14.626 --> 01:08:17.429
meaningless syllable came out of my mouth.

01:08:17.870 --> 01:08:19.131
And they said, all right, keep going.

01:08:20.893 --> 01:08:27.300
And like directly like some little just meaningless little words, syllables, not even words came out of my mouth.

01:08:27.320 --> 01:08:30.003
And they're like, yep, yep, yep, come on, come on, come on, come on.

01:08:30.363 --> 01:08:32.926
And it's just kind of like, I'm just saying it.

01:08:34.048 --> 01:08:38.973
And I thought, I don't know what this is, but I just need to get out of here and go home.

01:08:39.033 --> 01:08:43.538
So I'm not going to stop until they're satisfied, right?

01:08:43.714 --> 01:08:45.736
Now they're high-fiving each other.

01:08:47.178 --> 01:08:48.700
You know, oh, praise God, praise God.

01:08:49.220 --> 01:08:55.928
And in my mind, I know this kind of contradicts what I told you a second ago, but in my mind, I wasn't even fully convinced that's tongues.

01:08:56.809 --> 01:08:58.011
I was thinking, I don't know.

01:08:59.272 --> 01:09:02.776
And it seemed like the devil jumped on my shoulder and said, you're making that up.

01:09:04.619 --> 01:09:09.064
And it seemed like in the devil said to me, that's the blasphemy of the Holy Spirit.

01:09:09.364 --> 01:09:11.026
That's unforgivable sin.

01:09:11.490 --> 01:09:15.636
You know, now you're going to hell, but I just thought like, I don't care right now.

01:09:15.676 --> 01:09:17.038
Let me just get out of here.

01:09:18.360 --> 01:09:19.261
I'll deal with that later.

01:09:20.302 --> 01:09:24.768
I thought when I just get out of here and when I go home, I'll ask my pastor what he thinks about it.

01:09:24.788 --> 01:09:29.094
I'm so glad that didn't happen because I know what he would have told me.

01:09:30.937 --> 01:09:34.322
And so after a while, it just kept coming out.

01:09:34.382 --> 01:09:40.370
I'm speaking it, but I thought to myself, I don't think I'm smart enough to make this up.

01:09:42.786 --> 01:09:46.010
And I realized this is it.

01:09:46.390 --> 01:09:47.151
See, here's my problem.

01:09:48.252 --> 01:09:55.120
I thought I would be just taken over, like lose consciousness, you know, go up to the third heaven or something.

01:09:55.140 --> 01:09:58.603
And it was just like, I'm looking for Steven Spielberg.

01:10:01.466 --> 01:10:01.687
Right?

01:10:02.267 --> 01:10:04.270
And that's not exactly what it was.

01:10:05.191 --> 01:10:07.793
See, see, it says they're all filled and begin to speak in other tongues.

01:10:07.974 --> 01:10:09.155
It doesn't tell us how they felt.

01:10:11.558 --> 01:10:12.018
Why not?

01:10:12.098 --> 01:10:13.500
We don't really know.

01:10:14.622 --> 01:10:18.528
But the emphasis is not on how they felt, but what happened to them.

01:10:19.550 --> 01:10:19.870
You see?

01:10:20.571 --> 01:10:23.916
And so they told me, now don't stop speaking in tongues.

01:10:23.956 --> 01:10:24.658
Just keep doing it.

01:10:25.218 --> 01:10:26.180
So I was afraid to stop.

01:10:26.240 --> 01:10:28.203
I thought, if I stop, I'll never be able to do it again.

01:10:29.104 --> 01:10:32.690
So I drove home for like, you know, 45, 50 minutes from home speaking in tongues.

01:10:33.346 --> 01:10:36.291
And then I went in the back door of my parents' house.

01:10:36.311 --> 01:10:38.394
I didn't dare go in the front door speaking in tongues.

01:10:41.319 --> 01:10:43.503
They're going to call the pastor and we're going to have trouble.

01:10:43.884 --> 01:10:47.770
So I snuck in the back door, went up to my bedroom speaking in tongues.

01:10:48.111 --> 01:10:50.034
I knelt by the bed speaking in tongues.

01:10:50.562 --> 01:10:58.594
And then after a while, I was thirsty and I went down to the kitchen and I grabbed some water and when I drank a glass of water, I stopped because otherwise you'd be gargling in tongues.

01:10:58.614 --> 01:11:06.867
So I had to stop and then, you know, and then I went back up to the bedroom and lo and behold, I found out I can now do this when I want to.

01:11:10.473 --> 01:11:12.636
The Holy Spirit does not speak in tongues.

01:11:14.238 --> 01:11:16.041
We do.

01:11:16.061 --> 01:11:19.186
They were all filled and they

01:11:19.522 --> 01:11:20.443
began to speak.

01:11:21.545 --> 01:11:22.786
You see, you do the speaking.

01:11:23.888 --> 01:11:30.456
As the Spirit gave them utterance, one translation says, as the Holy Spirit allowed them to express themselves.

01:11:31.217 --> 01:11:36.224
See, He gave them the ability now to speak in this heavenly language.

01:11:36.244 --> 01:11:40.149
Speaking in tongues, it's not all God, and it's not all you, because it's your mouth.

01:11:41.411 --> 01:11:46.898
It's like your pipe is now connected to city water, but you control the tap.

01:11:47.426 --> 01:11:55.419
That's why some people get baptized all these spirits, speak in tongues, kick their heels, hooray, and then never speak in tongues again, because it's your mouth.

01:11:55.439 --> 01:11:57.142
You decide, you do the talking.

01:11:57.843 --> 01:12:11.645
I remember years ago, I took some friends to visit one Pentecostal church, and when the service was over, one young lady said to me, I have visited this church several times before.

01:12:11.665 --> 01:12:12.467
It's not my first time.

01:12:13.007 --> 01:12:14.610
And every time I come,

01:12:14.786 --> 01:12:17.969
I feel like I'm going to start speaking in tongues.

01:12:18.630 --> 01:12:23.274
And it's all I can do to not speak in tongues."

01:12:23.294 --> 01:12:26.197
And I said, Sister, you're not supposed to resist.

01:12:26.857 --> 01:12:28.279
You're supposed to yield.

01:12:29.120 --> 01:12:36.106
See, she thought like God hits you upside the head and grabs your tongue and you have no control.

01:12:36.146 --> 01:12:37.508
No, they began to speak.

01:12:37.588 --> 01:12:38.208
It's your mouth.

01:12:38.889 --> 01:12:44.274
Tongues doesn't come out of your stomach like a speaker box on the side of the wall here.

01:12:44.450 --> 01:12:46.773
It's you cooperating with the Holy Spirit.

01:12:47.614 --> 01:12:48.315
Are you listening to me?

01:12:49.217 --> 01:12:49.898
Are you listening to me?

01:12:50.979 --> 01:12:54.745
A lot of times people think, well, I'm not good enough to be filled with the Spirit.

01:12:55.405 --> 01:12:56.327
No one thought you were.

01:12:56.367 --> 01:13:01.214
Were you good enough to be saved?

01:13:02.395 --> 01:13:07.823
No, it's the Holy Spirit is not a reward for being a good Christian.

01:13:09.045 --> 01:13:12.850
Peter twice in the book of Acts refers to this as the gift

01:13:13.282 --> 01:13:14.323
of the Holy Spirit.

01:13:15.244 --> 01:13:16.846
Not a prize for great achievement.

01:13:17.287 --> 01:13:18.048
It's a gift.

01:13:18.669 --> 01:13:21.432
Let me give you one more verse because I don't need to look at the clock.

01:13:21.472 --> 01:13:22.854
I can just read your face.

01:13:23.234 --> 01:13:25.277
Notice just just one verse real quickly here.

01:13:25.837 --> 01:13:28.180
It's actually a couple of verses, but they're together.

01:13:28.200 --> 01:13:30.803
Luke 11 to 13.

01:13:31.584 --> 01:13:32.505
And we'll have to stop here.

01:13:33.486 --> 01:13:35.709
Luke 11 verse 11 to 13.

01:13:35.869 --> 01:13:36.931
What father among you?

01:13:36.971 --> 01:13:43.058
If his son asks for a fish, will instead of a fish give him a serpent?

01:13:44.258 --> 01:13:47.701
Or if he asks for an egg, we'll give him a scorpion.

01:13:48.722 --> 01:14:00.033
If you then who are evil know how to give good gifts to your children, how much more will the Heavenly Father give the Holy Spirit to those who ask him?

01:14:01.755 --> 01:14:13.426
Notice he didn't say how much more will your Heavenly Father give the Holy Spirit to those who are worthy, to those who are deserving, to those who have earned it, to those who ask.

01:14:14.466 --> 01:14:42.226
ask and I like this he said it he talks about a fish or an egg right he didn't say which of you if your son asked for a Lamborghini if your son asked for a Ferrari well if my son said I'd like to have a Lamborghini I probably say I'd like to have one too but you know even if even if my son misbehaved you know and it was not doing so well if he said

01:14:42.978 --> 01:14:44.079
Can I get an egg?

01:14:44.219 --> 01:14:45.360
I wouldn't say no.

01:14:46.602 --> 01:14:47.803
No, no, you're not worthy.

01:14:49.104 --> 01:14:50.986
I would say, yeah, sure, no problem.

01:14:51.426 --> 01:14:54.489
In other words, I wouldn't even have to think about it.

01:14:55.250 --> 01:14:55.590
Would you?

01:14:55.610 --> 01:15:03.518
I mean, that's not like some impossible thing that I would think like, you know, wait a minute, buddy.

01:15:03.538 --> 01:15:04.159
That's too much.

01:15:05.600 --> 01:15:11.346
For a Christian to ask the Father for the Holy Spirit, you don't need to convince him.

01:15:12.930 --> 01:15:14.251
He's already convinced.

01:15:15.152 --> 01:15:17.475
I'm not preaching to God this morning.

01:15:17.495 --> 01:15:18.596
I'm preaching to you.

01:15:18.656 --> 01:15:22.080
We are the ones who need to be convinced.

01:15:22.961 --> 01:15:23.982
Are you out there today?

01:15:24.002 --> 01:15:26.084
I said, are you out there today?

01:15:26.125 --> 01:15:27.746
Hallelujah.

01:15:28.727 --> 01:15:29.648
It's more than tongues.

01:15:31.130 --> 01:15:35.054
There came a boldness in my heart that I never had before.

01:15:36.376 --> 01:15:38.418
Boldness to share my testimony.

01:15:39.170 --> 01:15:47.944
How could I possibly go to the other side of the world to a people who don't even speak English by and large and totally different culture and everything?

01:15:48.705 --> 01:16:01.405
And sometimes you feel like you're the, and you are the only person there and they're just looking at you and preach God's truth because he, he clothed me with power from on high to him be the glory.

